        "timestamp": "2018-06-15 21:18:44.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Thanks Arash.  With this change is there any issue when there is a\n > corporate firewall?\n\nSorry I meant when there is *no* corporate firewall.",
