        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2018-06-15 22:09:23.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> > Thanks Arash.  With this change is there any issue when there is\n > a\n > > corporate firewall?\n > \n > Sorry I meant when there is *no* corporate firewall.\n\nThis is all based on system env variables http_proxy etc. So if there is no proxy these system env variables should not be set and this change should have no effect. But of course if the system env variables are set incorrectly then unit tests will fail just as they do today behind proxy without this change.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
