          "display_name": null,
          "email": "mhwang@research.att.com",
          "username": "researchmike"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-06-18 14:04:11.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+2\n\n> > > Thanks Arash.  With this change is there any issue when there\n > is\n > > a\n > > > corporate firewall?\n > >\n > > Sorry I meant when there is *no* corporate firewall.\n > \n > This is all based on system env variables http_proxy etc. So if\n > there is no proxy these system env variables should not be set and\n > this change should have no effect. But of course if the system env\n > variables are set incorrectly then unit tests will fail just as\n > they do today behind proxy without this change.\n\nOk thanks for the clarification",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
